{"tid":2403222,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"WFH被咁玩法，係咪搵定工轉都得？","createTime":"2021-02-11T03:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T07:48:42.000Z","uid":230762,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad00540792ed7e8f1ed0cd431e2f636c7f2c7ee6","tid":2403222,"uid":230762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"小薯一名，間中出街跑腿，但唔係主要工作。<br />\n<br />\n疫情期間，公司跟政府行roster。第1-3波都叫正常，第4波開始比人玩野，就係我WFH時，經常叫我做跑腿，係本來唔使返工，都要返office收件再去跑。<br />\n<br />\nWFH原意，唔係希望員工盡量留屋企，減少出外逼黨鐵逼巴士咩？又要員工WFH，又要WFH既員工跑街，係咪自打咀巴？<br />\n<br />\n最吊跪係，呢D跑街order，只在我WFH時出現。roster編我返工時，就一定唔叫我跑街，有野要出，就搵速遞公司。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣擺明玩野，我係咪搵定工轉都得？"},{"pid":"d5145e122b0ab4313013a9d9b642aeb5d63c452b","tid":2403222,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"全公司人淨係玩你一個？"},{"pid":"403ff9273993270e4292ed8f3df5789a848569cf","tid":2403222,"uid":30028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"唔高興咪轉囉"},{"pid":"14c721cfbb95bc0a06c590837c9ca26c472e9633","tid":2403222,"uid":19166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"cu？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce771e1212cfdb8431bc53286ef11edebb30883f","tid":2403222,"uid":362459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"你覺得你做既野同收入唔成正比 係蝕既你咪走"},{"pid":"eef3558e173f64053305b9420d07818f96936fa1","tid":2403222,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T07:48:42.000Z","msg":"wfh 既意思係彈性安排工作"}]}